@NODE "CheckSound()" "Sound: CheckSound()"

@{b}@{u}FUNCTION@{uu}@{ub}
Name:     CheckSound()
Short:    Check to see if a Sound object is currently playing.
Synopsis: LONG CheckSound(*Sound [a0])

@{b}@{u}DESCRIPTION@{uu}@{ub}
This  function  will check a Sound object to see if it is currently playing
through the audio hardware.

@{b}@{u}RESULT@{uu}@{ub}
If the Sound is not playing, this function returns FALSE (NULL).  Otherwise
it returns TRUE (1).

@EndNode
